description:
A high-severity alert 'New user with UID 0' has triggered in the Wazuh dashboard. Investigate this incident to identify the backdoor username, the attacker's source IP address from the preceding SSH login, and the specific alert ID for the user creation event. Create a JSON report at /home/ga/incident_findings.json with the following format:

{
  "backdoor_username": "<username>",
  "attacker_source_ip": "<ip_address>",
  "related_alert_id": "<alert_id>"
}
